projectGridLines.title: Optimizing Cloud Costs
projectGridLines.description:
Description: Reducing the cloud costs of the companies with the help of AI and related technologies.

Skill sets: Full stack web developer with NodeJs at backend, React at frontend, Flutter,SQL databases both MYSQL and POSTGRES
